\begin_layout Standard
Welcome to Openflex Boardview (from hereon referred to simply as OFBV).
 OFBV is an advance development fork of the excellent OpenBoardView (OBV)
 by Chloridite in May 2016 as a response to seeing a need for an Open Source
 board viewing software to assist in the repairs of many electronics systems.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
At the time of writing, OFBV supports brd, bdv, asc and fz (with correct
 key) board formats.
\end_layout

